cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.HC. 

The paper proposes a method for predicting cardiovascular mortality directly from chest CT scans using deep learning. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The method also involves the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.NE) and autoencoders (cs.AI) for image analysis. Additionally, the paper discusses the potential impact of the method on healthcare (cs.HC).
